{"type":"message","id":"ccbd80f5","parentId":"fac019fb","timestamp":"2026-04-08T05:59:10.308Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"问题在于：\n1. 虚拟环境的akshare有问题（网络代理问题）\n2. Python 3.14系统环境可以运行，但缺少pct_change列\n\n关键数据：\n- 4月7日上证收盘3890.165\n- 4月3日上证收盘3880.097\n- 4月2日上证收盘3919.285\n\n从K线数据看，4月7日（清明后第一个交易日）上证收盘3890，比4月3日3880涨约0.26%，涨幅不大\n\n但用户说\"大盘大涨\"，可能指的是：\n1. 今天（4月8日）的实时涨幅（我无法获取）\n2. 港股/美股今天大涨\n3. 用户看到的是其他指数\n\n让我尝试直接获取今天的数据，或者获取个股情况来验证。\n","thinkingSignature":"dea1fb340ab575f75de74663c36e6158b380c48c7895d50d23936717cb35269a"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_qw8e7vrx82wc_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"/Library/Frameworks/Python.framework/Versions/3.14/bin/python3.14 -c \"\nimport akshare as ak\n\n# 获取个股涨跌情况来判断\nprint('=== 个股涨跌统计 ===')\n\n# 尝试使用另一个接口\ntry:\n    # 这个接口可能更稳定\n    df = ak.stock_zh_a_spot_em()\n    # 计算涨跌\n    up = len(df[df['涨跌幅'] > 0])\n    down = len(df[df['涨跌幅'] < 0])\n    flat = len(df[df['涨跌幅'] == 0])\n    total = len(df)\n    print(f'上涨: {up} ({up/total*100:.1f}%)')\n    print(f'下跌: {down} ({down/total*100:.1f}%)')\n    print(f'平盘: {flat}')\n    \n    # 涨幅前10\n    print('\\n涨幅前10:')\n    top10 = df.nlargest(10, '涨跌幅')\n    print(top10[['代码','名称','最新价','涨跌幅']].to_string())\nexcept Exception as e:\n    print(f'获取失败: {e}')\n\" 2>&1","timeout":90}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":410,"output":455,"cacheRead":36288,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37153,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775627932163,"responseId":"0625219cdd2bab931ca33c999cea50a5"}}
