{"type":"message","id":"8fad80e0","parentId":"771fa76b","timestamp":"2026-04-08T08:47:22.165Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说\"今天开盘啊\"，意思是今天（4月8日）开盘时大盘是大涨的。让我重新理解这个问题 - 用户可能在开盘时看到了大盘大涨，但某个系统给出了\"防守观察\"的建议，所以感到困惑。\n\n让我尝试获取今天开盘的数据，或者查看是否有今日开盘信息。\n","thinkingSignature":"0583ef9c2756b35d69b1c91ce24b28bffc927cc26aa3a344c58ed2b3665348af"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_3zdummidmv6r_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"/Library/Frameworks/Python.framework/Versions/3.14/bin/python3.14 -c \"\nimport akshare as ak\nfrom datetime import datetime\n\n# 获取上证指数历史数据，看4月8日\ndf = ak.stock_zh_index_daily(symbol='sh000001')\n\n# 找到4月8日的数据\nfor idx, row in df.iterrows():\n    if '2026-04-08' in str(row['date']):\n        print(f\\\"4月8日 上证: 开={row['open']} 高={row['high']} 低={row['low']} 收={row['close']}\\\")\n        prev = df.iloc[idx-1] if idx > 0 else None\n        if prev is not None:\n            change = (row['close'] - prev['close']) / prev['close'] * 100\n            print(f\\\"对比4月7日收盘 {prev['close']}: 涨跌幅={change:.2f}%\\\")\n        break\nelse:\n    # 如果没有4月8日，看看最新数据\n    print('最新数据:')\n    print(df.tail(3).to_string())\n\" 2>&1","timeout":20}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":36656,"output":344,"cacheRead":1088,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38088,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775638020473,"responseId":"062549042c260f83abcf0e14260b79df"}}
