{"type":"message","id":"b7f51e1f","parentId":"3de4cdc2","timestamp":"2026-04-08T09:34:12.692Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_5578e37bd0684a3fa6c84f72","toolName":"tavily_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"\\\"Everything Claude Code\\\" github repository\",\n  \"provider\": \"tavily\",\n  \"count\": 5,\n  \"tookMs\": 1617,\n  \"externalContent\": {\n    \"untrusted\": true,\n    \"source\": \"web_search\",\n    \"provider\": \"tavily\",\n    \"wrapped\": true\n  },\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"94106ebc43bec99c\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nEverything Claude Code hits 100K stars: what developers should ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"94106ebc43bec99c\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.augmentcode.com/learn/everything-claude-code-github\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"49993861c629e9cf\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nThe affaan-m/everything-claude-code GitHub repo showing 100K stars, 13K forks, 768 commits, and folder structure including agents, hooks, rules, and skills. Everything Claude Code (ECC) provides is a structured layer of skills, rules, hooks, security scanning, and memory persistence that works across Claude Code, Cursor, Codex, and OpenCode. Teams get shared rules across tools, security guardrails that block common agent misbehaviors, and a hook system that enforces TDD and code review without manual oversight. With 113 contributors and translations in seven languages, ECC has become a community standard for agent configuration, the **.editorconfig** equivalent for AI coding tools. When a developer uses Claude Code to add an authentication endpoint, the TDD agent enforces write-tests-first. Claude Code is ECC's primary target, with full coverage: 28 agents, 60 commands, 34 rules, and 8 hook event types. According to the project's feature parity table, OpenCode supports 11 hook events and 6 native custom tools, more than Claude Code in those specific areas, but fewer total agents (12 vs.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"49993861c629e9cf\\\">>>\",\n      \"score\": 0.9075175\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"aee691f8e00182aa\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nEverything Claude Code GitHub Repository: https ... - Facebook\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"aee691f8e00182aa\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.facebook.com/techieprogrammer016/videos/everything-claude-code-github-repository-httpsgithubcomaffaan-meverything-claude/1332856312007721/\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"a00851e216b491ec\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nEverything Claude Code GitHub Repository: https://github.com/affaan-m/everything-claude-code.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"a00851e216b491ec\\\">>>\",\n      \"score\": 0.8571119\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"553c4b2e00454a45\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nWorldFlowAI/everything-claude-code: Claude Code toolkit - GitHub\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"553c4b2e00454a45\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://github.com/worldflowai/everything-claude-code\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"245967aa26b4418e\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nThe complete collection of Claude Code configs from an Anthropic hackathon winner. Production-ready agents, skills, hooks, commands, rules, and MCP\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"245967aa26b4418e\\\">>>\",\n      \"score\": 0.84215075\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"b97adf549952f535\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\naffaan-m/everything-claude-code: The agent harness ... - GitHub\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"b97adf549952f535\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://github.com/affaan-m/everything-claude-code\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNA