ude Code is ECC's primary target, with full coverage: 28 agents, 60 commands, 34 rules, and 8 hook event types. According to the project's feature parity table, OpenCode supports 11 hook events and 6 native custom tools, more than Claude Code in those specific areas, but fewer total agents (12 vs.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"49993861c629e9cf\">>>","score":0.9075175},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"aee691f8e00182aa\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nEverything Claude Code GitHub Repository: https ... - Facebook\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"aee691f8e00182aa\">>>","url":"https://www.facebook.com/techieprogrammer016/videos/everything-claude-code-github-repository-httpsgithubcomaffaan-meverything-claude/1332856312007721/","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"a00851e216b491ec\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nEverything Claude Code GitHub Repository: https://github.com/affaan-m/everything-claude-code.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"a00851e216b491ec\">>>","score":0.8571119},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"553c4b2e00454a45\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nWorldFlowAI/everything-claude-code: Claude Code toolkit - GitHub\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"553c4b2e00454a45\">>>","url":"https://github.com/worldflowai/everything-claude-code","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"245967aa26b4418e\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nThe complete collection of Claude Code configs from an Anthropic hackathon winner. Production-ready agents, skills, hooks, commands, rules, and MCP\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"245967aa26b4418e\">>>","score":0.84215075},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"b97adf549952f535\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\naffaan-m/everything-claude-code: The agent harness ... - GitHub\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"b97adf549952f535\">>>","url":"https://github.com/affaan-m/everything-claude-code","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"aac4e8e037245319\">>>\nSou