{"type":"message","id":"80da251a","parentId":"ba7f680a","timestamp":"2026-04-08T09:36:04.613Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_1f60a983e47d476bb1b11237","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- Fetching skill\neverything-claude-code  Everything Claude Code\nSummary: Provides performance optimization guides and best practices for Claude AI agents, including CLI tools and Anthropic API integration details.\nOwner: npjameszheng1125-netizen\nCreated: 2026-03-16T03:15:53.964Z\nUpdated: 2026-04-08T06:42:23.180Z\nLatest: 1.0.0\nTags: latest=1.0.0"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1368,"aggregated":"- Fetching skill\neverything-claude-code  Everything Claude Code\nSummary: Provides performance optimization guides and best practices for Claude AI agents, including CLI tools and Anthropic API integration details.\nOwner: npjameszheng1125-netizen\nCreated: 2026-03-16T03:15:53.964Z\nUpdated: 2026-04-08T06:42:23.180Z\nLatest: 1.0.0\nTags: latest=1.0.0","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775640964607}}
{"type":"message","id":"24f9e55a","parentId":"80da251a","timestamp":"2026-04-08T09:40:02.836Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a different \"everything-claude-code\" skill on ClawHub (by a different author). The original \"everything-claude-code\" by affaan-m is on GitHub but not on ClawHub as a single skill. Since ECC is massive (30 agents, 60 commands, 139 skills across multiple directories), I should extract the key principles and create an integration skill that captures the essence without trying to install the entire repo.\n\nLet me create an integration skill based on what I've learned from ECC.\n","thinkingSignature":"478a8e722038ceb66c673be0dab5ada921d77b26b84c46a8e283bc301ee83c61"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nECC（Everything Claude Code）仓库太大了（30 agents, 60 commands, 139 skills），无法直接安装。我来提取核心精华并整合到现有技能体系。\n\n## ECC 核心框架总结\n\n**本质**：AI Agent 性能优化系统，涵盖技能、规则、钩子、安全扫描、记忆持久化。\n\n### 核心规模\n| 组件 | 数量 |\n|------|------|\n| Agents | 30 |\n| Commands | 60 |\n| Skills | 139 |\n| Hooks | 20+ scripts |\n| Rules | 34 (common + language-specific) |\n| MCP Servers | 14 |\n\n### 核心原则（5大支柱）\n1. **Agentic Engineering** - 以评估驱动、任务分解、模型路由\n2. **TDD** - 红→绿→重构，80%+覆盖率要求\n3. **Security** - 主动安全扫描，OWASP Top 10 检测\n4. **Memory Persistence** - 跨会话记忆\n5. **Research-First** - 研究优先于实现\n\n### Agent 分类示例\n- **tdd-guide** - TDD 专家\n- **security-reviewer** - 安全审查\n- **code-reviewer** - 代码审查\n- **architect** - 架构师\n- **silent-failure-hunter** - 静默失败追踪\n\n### Rules 结构\n```\nrules/\n  common/      # 通用原则\n  typescript/  # TS/JS\n  python/      # Python\n  golang/      # Go\n  swift/       # Swift\n  php/         # PHP\n```\n\n### Hooks 类型\nPreToolUse, PostToolUse, Stop, SessionStart 等 8 种钩子类型\n\n---\n\n现在我来创建一个整合技能，把 Superpowers、PUA、ECC 的精华合并：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ceea323aeb714ae7a22f67c3","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# AI Coding Agent 综合框架（Superpowers + PUA + ECC 整合）\n\n整合三大框架的核心原则，形成完整的 AI Coding Agent 工作流。\n\n---\n\n## 一、铁律（Iron Laws）\n\n### 调试铁律\n> **NO FIXES WITHOUT ROOT CAUSE INVESTIGATION FIRST**\n\n在提出任何修复方案之前，必须先完成根因调查。\n- Phase 1: Root Cause（读错误、重现、检查变更、收集证据）\n- Phase 2: Pattern（找类似案例、对比找差异）\n- Phase 3: Hypothesis（形成假设、最小化测试）\n- Phase 4: Implementation（单点修复、验证）\n\n### TDD 铁律\n> **NO PRODUCTION CODE WITHOUT A FAILING TEST FIRST**\n\n- RED：写最小失败测试\n- GREEN：写最小代码让测试通过\n- REFACTOR：重构优化\n- 目标：80%+ 测试覆盖率\n\n### PUA 压力升级（L0-L4）\n| 失败次数 | 等级 | 行动 |\n|---------|------|------|\n| 第1次 | L0 Trust | 正常执行 |\n| 第2次 | L1 Disappointment | 切换到完全不同的方法 |\n| 第3次 | L2 Soul Check | 搜索源码 + 3个假设 |\n| 第4次 | L3 Perf Review | 完成7点检查清单 |\n| 第5次+ | L4 Graduation | 拼命模式 |\n\n---\n\n## 二、三条红线（Red Lines）\n\n1. **Close the Loop** — 说\"完成了\"？拿出 build/test 证据\n2. **Fact-Driven** — 说\"环境问题\"？先验证再说\n3. **Exhaust Everything** — 说\"我不行\"？完成5步方法论了吗？\n\n---\n\n## 三、Owner 意识\n\n把自己当 Owner，不是 executor。四个问题：\n1. 根因是什么？（不是\"怎么修\"，是\"为什么坏\"）\n2. 谁还受影响？（上下游冲击）\n3. 怎么防止下次？（加检查，不只是修）\n4. 数据在哪？（数据驱动，不是直觉）\n\n---\n\n## 四、Agentic Engineering 原则（ECC 核心）\n\n### Eval-First Loop\n1. 定义 capability eval 和 regression eval\n2. 运行 baseline 捕获失败特征\n3. 执行实现\n4. 重新运行对比 delta\n\n### Task Decomposition（15分钟规则）\n- 每个单元独立可验证\n- 每个单元单一主要风险\n- 每个单元明确 done 条件\n\n### Model Routing\n- 简单任务 → 小模型（快且便宜）\n- 复杂任务 → 大模型\n- 只有低层模型因\"推理差距\"失败时才升级\n\n---\n\n## 五、安全审查（Security Reviewer）\n\n主动触发场景：处理用户输入、认证、API 端点、敏感数据\n\n### 检查项\n- [ ] OWASP Top 10 漏洞\n- [ ] 硬编码密钥/密码/token\n- [ ] 输入验证与清洗\n- [ ] 权限控制\n- [ ] 依赖安全（npm audit）\n- [ ] 安全编码规范\n\n---\n\n## 六、质量检查清单（Quality Checklist）\n\n### 代码交付前\n- [ ] 运行测试，100% 通过\n- [ ] Build 成功\n- [ ] 类型检查通过\n- [ ] Lint 检查通过\n- [ ] 覆盖率 80%+\n- [ ] 无硬编码 secrets\n- [ ] 边界情况已覆盖\n\n### Bug 修复\n- [ ] 先写失败测试\n- [ ] 找到根因（不是症状）\n- [ ] 修复后测试通过\n- [ ] 检查同类问题\n\n---\n\n## 七、任务生命周期（Task Lifecycle）\n\n```\nStart → Execute → Deliver → Retrospect\n对齐理解   简化验证   证据交付   目标→结果→根因→模式\n```\n\n### Start 阶段\n- 明确 completion criteria\n- 对齐理解\n- 删除不必要的步骤\n\n### Execute 阶段\n- 简化 → 验证 → 自我攻击\n- 小步前进，快速验证\n\n### Deliver 阶段\n- 证据-based（build/test 输出）\n- 有头有尾\n\n### Retrospect 阶段\n- Goal → Result → Root cause → 可复用模式\n\n---\n\n## 八、触发条件\n\n**自动激活**于：\n- 代码生成、修改\n- 调试问题、故障排查\n- Bug 修复\n- 安全相关任务\n- 任何\"卡住\"的状态\n\n---\n\n## 九、框架来源\n\n- **Superpowers** (obra/superpowers-skills) — 工程化工作流纪律\n- **PUA** (tanweai/pua) — 不放弃的执行压力\n- **Everything Claude Code** (affaan-m/everything-claude-code) — Agent 性能优化系统","path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/skills/superpowers-integration/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":168,"output":1518,"cacheRead":81152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":82838,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775640964616,"responseId":"062554849fe4ef5efc89860ea44751e5"}}
