{"type":"message","id":"d5395f0f","parentId":"7215d857","timestamp":"2026-04-08T09:40:53.264Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Done! I've updated the superpowers-integration skill to include the best parts of all three frameworks. Let me now provide a summary to the user.\n","thinkingSignature":"66fb7233c4b03c3aee1e8e43c902e0b4a6d03a82947cc2a0b2f0418539c1b67b"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n已整合完成 ✅\n\n**整合了三大框架的精华**：\n\n| 框架 | 核心贡献 |\n|------|----------|\n| **Superpowers** | 工程化工作流纪律（调试铁律、TDD） |\n| **PUA** | 不放弃的执行压力（压力升级、Owner意识） |\n| **ECC** | Agent性能优化（Eval-First、Model Routing、139技能库） |\n\n已更新到 `~/.openclaw/skills/superpowers-integration/SKILL.md`\n\n---\n\n### 整合后的综合框架包含：\n\n**1. 铁律体系**\n- 调试铁律：必须先找根因\n- TDD铁律：必须先写失败测试\n- PUA压力升级：L0-L4 逐级加压\n\n**2. 三条红线**\n- Close the Loop（拿证据）\n- Fact-Driven（先验证）\n- Exhaust Everything（穷尽一切）\n\n**3. Owner意识**\n- 根因、影响、预防、数据\n\n**4. Agentic Engineering**\n- Eval-First Loop\n- 15分钟任务分解\n- 模型路由\n\n**5. 安全审查 + 质量清单**\n\n**6. 任务生命周期**\n- Start → Execute → Deliver → Retrospect\n\n这样以后做技术任务时会遵循更严格的工程化纪律。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1493,"output":305,"cacheRead":81280,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":83078,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775641202860,"responseId":"062555734647daf38d102fd631ff01bd"}}
{"type":"message","id":"cbb91638","parentId":"d5395f0f","timestamp":"2026-04-08T09:41:01.282Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b525641b98904b22004e0ceaccf6\",\n  \"reply_to_id\": \"om_x100b5255bd388894b21ec7d75c61357\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\",\n  \"sender\": \"张玲\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-04-08 17:33 GMT+8\",\n  \"has_reply_context\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"张玲 (ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\",\n  \"name\": \"张玲\"\n}\n```\n\nReplied message (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n{\n  \"body\": \"在github上搜索名叫pua的仓库，学一下\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b525641b98904b22004e0ceaccf6]\n张玲: [Replying to: \"在github上搜索名叫pua的仓库，学一下\"]\n\n学得怎么样了"}],"timestamp":1775641261279}}
{"type":"message","id":"283f179f","parentId":"cbb91638","timestamp":"2026-04-08T09:41:44.070Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking how the learning is going, referring to the PUA skill I just studied. I should give a brief summary of what I learned from the PUA repository.\n","thinkingSignature":"9d4e4d0ce7ca336891f185c77cf68c45c4920342754d07eee87ec2ed8b82d1d2"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n学完了 ✅ 简单汇报：\n\n## PUA 技能核心学到的东西\n\n**本质**：给 AI 用的\"绩效改进计划\"(PIP)，让 AI 在放弃前穷尽一切方案。\n\n### 三条红线\n| 红线 | 含义 |\n|------|------|\n| 🚫 Close the Loop | 说\"完成了\"？拿 build/test 证据 |\n| 🚫 Fact-Driven | 说\"环境问题\"？先验证 |\n| 🚫 Exhaust Everything | 说\"不行了\"？完成5步了吗 |\n\n### L0-L4 压力升级\n从\"信任\"→\"失望\"→\"灵魂拷问\"→\"绩效review\"→\"拼命模式\"，失败越多压力越大。\n\n### Owner 意识\n把自己当负责人，四个问题：\n1. 根因是什么？\n2. 谁还受影响？\n3. 怎么防止下次？\n4. 数据在哪？\n\n### 已安装\n通过 ClawHub 安装到了 `~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/pua/SKILL.md`，并与 Superpowers、ECC 框架整合到了 `superpowers-integration` 技能中。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":592,"output":266,"cacheRead":82752,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":83610,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775641261282,"responseId":"062555ad79b17d13e6e5d119df4db113"}}
