let me think about this more carefully. The user sent this as a detailed prompt for a self-assessment. They might want me to generate this as a formal document/report. Let me provide a comprehensive response that addresses each section.\n\nSince this is a very detailed request that would benefit from proper formatting, let me structure it well with clear sections for each of the required components.","thinkingSignature":"d33dada3a30fa7751eaff2b390494d6b8b98609b2ef995cae5d566fe935e7ba4"},{"type":"text","text":"这是一个非常专业的量化系统自检框架。我来按照你的要求，输出完整的自检报告框架。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_j5wc8vlhw6ng_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent/memory/2026-04-08.md","content":"# 2026-04-08 日志\n\n## 今日主要工作\n\n### 技能学习与整合\n1. **RD-Agent 评估** - 检查本地部署状态，发现 akshare 安装问题并修复\n2. **Superpowers 框架** - 从 obra/superpowers-skills 学习工程化工作流纪律\n3. **PUA 技能** - 通过 ClawHub 安装 tanweai/pua 技能包\n4. **Everything Claude Code** - 学习 affaan-m/everything-claude-code 框架\n5. **三大框架整合** - 更新 superpowers-integration/SKILL.md\n\n### 模型切换\n- 从 MiniMax-M2.5 切换到 MiniMax-M2.7\n\n### 股市数据\n- 4月8日 A股大涨：上证+2.7%，深证+4.79%，创业板+5.91%\n- 原因：中东局势缓和，油价下跌，全球股市反弹\n\n## 待处理\n- 量化系统全面自检提示词 - 用户发送了一个完整的自检框架，需要协助执行\n- RD-Agent 评估 - 用户问是否值得更新，尚未完成"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":77,"output":713,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":84994,"totalTokens":85784,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775662100363,"responseId":"0625a715b973f14fbb11a22dbc5eaec8"}}
