{"type":"message","id":"fe7107d4","parentId":"c9a505a1","timestamp":"2026-04-08T15:49:10.288Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is pointing out that I presented those numbers as if they were facts from their actual situation, but actually I was just giving an example of what typically happens. I need to be honest and clarify that those numbers were illustrative examples, not their actual data.\n\nThis is actually a good example of the PUA \"Fact-Driven\" principle - I should have stated clearly that those were hypothetical examples, not their actual numbers.\n\nLet me respond honestly.","thinkingSignature":"15290dabdd0e96c73194e43545e91847e5d9ecad3a379f3d42ebabb6d9c72204"},{"type":"text","text":"你说得对，我应该诚实说明：\n\n**那些数字是我举例说明，不是你的真实数据。**\n\n我当时写的是：\n> \"回测年化 30%，实盘仅 12%，偏差率 65%，大概率存在过拟合或滑点低估\"\n\n这是**典型的回测-实盘偏差场景举例**，不是你的实际数字。\n\n---\n\n这是我的问题：\n\n1. **表达不清** - 没有说清楚这是\"假设案例\"\n2. **违反了 Fact-Driven 原则** - 说了\"大概率存在\"但没数据支撑\n\n---\n\n**需要你告诉我的**：\n\n1. 你的策略回测业绩是多少？\n2. 实盘业绩是多少？\n3. 最大回撤回测 vs 实盘分别是多少？\n\n这样我才能帮你做**真实的归因分析**，而不是空对空。\n\n另外，今天已经很晚了（23:48），如果你困了明天继续也行，不用硬撑着。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":77,"output":277,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":92993,"totalTokens":93347,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775663337916,"responseId":"0625abead3915082fef861c502c7113e"}}
