{"type":"message","id":"616773be","parentId":"4fb93d13","timestamp":"2026-04-08T16:26:56.810Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK, so the cost prices in this ledger seem to be the current market values (not the original cost basis), because all the \"pnl\" is showing 0. This is probably the \"market value\" column from the ledger, not the actual cost. \n\nWait, looking more carefully:\n- A股+港股持仓市值: 1,802,479\n- A股+港股成本: 1,802,479 (same number!)\n- ETF基金市值: 642,282\n- Total: 2,444,760\n- Cash: 880,000\n- Total assets: ~3.3 million\n\n\n- This doesn't make sense with the user's statement that only 880,000 cash remains. If the holdings are showing the same values for both market value and cost, these must be current values, not original purchase prices. The ledger probably just returns the current position values rather than historical cost basis.\n\n- Now I need to understand what the quantity column actually represents and whether I can cross-reference this with the ths_selected_holdings file that had the cost information.","thinkingSignature":"6fc6ade286866529233979dabe1c1eab1f704f78bdcbb96b910973f333160627"},{"type":"text","text":"价格全是0，说明akshare今天获取不到。让我直接从THS的CSV文件计算（那里面有成本价）。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ty0mz3t86pmm_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"/Library/Frameworks/Python.framework/Versions/3.14/bin/python3.14 << 'EOF'\nimport akshare as ak\nimport pandas as pd\n\n# 从THS导出文件获取成本价\ndf = pd.read_csv('/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent/ths_selected_holdings.csv')\nprint(f\"总持仓: {len(df)}个\\n\")\n\n# 只处理A股，不处理ETF和名字是nan的\nresults = []\nfor _, row in df.iterrows():\n    code = row['symbol']\n    name = row['name']\n    qty = float(row['quantity'])\n    cost = float(row['cost_price'])\n    asset_type = row.get('asset_type', 'stock')\n    \n    if asset_type == 'fund' or 'nan' in str(name):\n        continue\n    \n    # A股获取最新价\n    try:\n        pure = code.replace('.SH','').replace('.SZ','')\n        df_quote = ak.stock_bid_ask_em(symbol=pure)\n        quote = {r['item']: r['value'] for _, r in df_quote.iterrows()}\n        current = float(quote.get('最新', 0))\n        chg = float(quote.get('涨幅', 0))\n        if current == 0:\n            raise ValueError(\"price=0\")\n    except:\n        try:\n            df_hist = ak.stock_zh_a_hist(symbol=pure, period='daily', adjust='qfq')\n            current = float(df_hist.iloc[-1]['close'])\n            prev = float(df_hist.iloc[-2]['close']) if len(df_hist) > 1 else current\n            chg = round((current-prev)/prev*100, 2)\n        except:\n            current = cost\n            chg = 0\n    \n    mv = qty * current\n    cost_basis = qty * cost\n    pnl = mv - cost_basis\n    pnl_pct = round((current - cost) / cost * 100, 1) if cost > 0 else 0\n    results.append({\n        'name': name, 'code': code, 'qty': int(qty), \n        'cost': cost, 'current': round(current, 3), \n        'chg_today': round(chg, 2),\n        'mv': round(mv, 0), 'pnl': round(pnl, 0), 'pnl_pct': pnl_pct\n    })\n\n# 按亏损排序\nresults.sort(key=lambda x: x['pnl_pct'])\n\nprint(\"=\" * 70)\nprint(f\"{'股票':<8} {'名称':<8} {'数量':>6} {'成本':>8} {'现价':>8} {'今日':>6} {'市值':>10} {'盈亏额':>10} {'盈亏%':>6}\")\nprint(\"=\" * 70)\n\ntotal_mv = 0\ntotal_cost = 0\ntotal_pnl = 0\n\nfor r in results:\n    flag = \"🔴\" if r['pnl_pct'] < -10 else \"🟡\" if r['pnl_pct'] < 0 else \"🟢\"\n    print(f\"{flag}{r['code']:<6} {r['name']:<8} {r['qty']:>6} {r['cost']:>8.2f} {r['current']:>8.3f} {r['chg_today']:>+6.1f}% {r['mv']:>10,.0f} {r['pnl']:>>+10,.0f} {r['pnl_pct']:>+6.1f}%\")\n    total_mv += r['mv']\n    total_cost += r['qty'] * r['cost']\n    total_pnl += r['pnl']\n\nprint(\"=\" * 70)\nprint(f\"总计: 市值={total_mv:,.0f} 成本={total_cost:,.0f} 盈亏={total_pnl:,.0f} ({total_pnl/total_cost*100:+.1f}%)\")\nprint(f\"\\n股票数量: {len(results)}只\")\nEOF\n","timeout":120}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":116209,"outpu