{"type":"message","id":"2b4560da","parentId":"c3b5a8d2","timestamp":"2026-04-08T16:29:06.894Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see there are 3 ledger accounts:\n1. `12065413` - 26 holdings (23 A-shares, 2 HK, 1 fund) - This might be the older snapshot\n2. `2269916` - 36 holdings (30 A-shares, 2 HK, 4 funds) - This is the bigger account\n3. `301719457562` - 1 holding (600363.SH 联创光电) - Small account\n\nThe user said there are ~88万 cash and about 12万 in stocks (based on total ~100万 assets). But the current prices of stocks may have changed a lot.\n\n\nThe real problem is that the `cost_price` field in the ledger export contains current market values, not historical purchase costs. I should check the local THS holdings file instead, which should have the actual cost basis data.","thinkingSignature":"52441bb87c919ffb4451cee81fe03694752b7a29be94227ef83c77d67f134b25"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，skill完美抓到了3个账户！让我用之前那个有真实成本价的文件来算盈亏。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_p44u13p8gb6i_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"/Library/Frameworks/Python.framework/Versions/3.14/bin/python3.14 << 'PYEOF'\nimport akshare as ak\nimport pandas as pd\n\n# 使用有真实成本价的文件\ndf = pd.read_csv('/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/ths_selected_holdings_20260401.csv')\nprint(f\"持仓: {len(df)}只\\n\")\nprint(\"原始数据示例:\")\nprint(df.head(5).to_string())\nprint()\n\nresults = []\nfor _, row in df.iterrows():\n    code = row['symbol']\n    qty = float(row['quantity'])\n    cost = float(row['cost_price'])\n    \n    if qty <= 0: continue\n    \n    # 获取名称和现价\n    try:\n        pure = code.replace('.SH','').replace('.SZ','')\n        \n        # 获取名称\n        try:\n            df_info = ak.stock_individual_info_em(symbol=pure)\n            name = df_info[df_info['item']=='股票简称'].iloc[0]['value']\n        except:\n            name = code\n        \n        # 获取现价\n        try:\n            df_quote = ak.stock_bid_ask_em(symbol=pure)\n            quote = {r['item']: r['value'] for _, r in df_quote.iterrows()}\n            current = float(quote.get('最新', 0))\n            chg = float(quote.get('涨幅', 0))\n            if current == 0: raise ValueError(\"0\")\n        except:\n            try:\n                df_hist = ak.stock_zh_a_hist(symbol=pure, period='daily', adjust='qfq')\n                current = float(df_hist.iloc[-1]['close'])\n                prev = float(df_hist.iloc[-2]['close']) if len(df_hist)>1 else current\n                chg = round((current-prev)/prev*100, 1)\n            except:\n                current = cost; chg = 0\n    except:\n        name = code; current = cost; chg = 0\n    \n    mv = qty * current\n    cost_mv = qty * cost\n    pnl = mv - cost_mv\n    pnl_pct = round((current-cost)/cost*100, 1) if cost > 0 else 0\n    \n    results.append({\n        'code': code, 'name': name, 'qty': int(qty),\n        'cost': cost, 'current': round(current, 3),\n        'chg': round(chg, 1),\n        'mv': round(mv, 0), 'cost_mv': round(cost_mv, 0),\n        'pnl': round(pnl, 0), 'pnl_pct': pnl_pct\n    })\n\nresults.sort(key=lambda x: x['pnl_pct'])\n\n# 计算（4月1日至今已一周，用4月1日收盘价代替今日）\nprint(\"=\" * 75)\nprint(f\"{'代码':<10} {'名称':<8} {'数量':>6} {'成本':>8} {'4月1日价':>10} {'盈亏%':>7} {'市值':>10} {'盈亏额':>10}\")\nprint(\"=\" * 75)\n\ntotal_mv = total_cost = total_pnl = 0\nfor r in results:\n    e = \"🔴\" if r['pnl_pct'] < -15 else \"🟡\" if r['pnl_pct'] < 0 else \"🟢\"\n    print(f\"{e}{r['code']:<10} {r['name']:<8} {r['qty']:>6} {r['cost']:>8.2f} {r['current']:>10.3f} {r['pnl_pct']:>+6.1f}% {r['mv']:>10,.0f} {r['pnl']:>+10,.0f}\")\n    total_mv += r['mv']\n    total_cost += r['cost_mv']\n    total_pnl += r['pnl']\n\nprint(\"=\" * 75)\nprint(f\"持仓市值: {total_mv:,.0f} | 持仓成本: {total_cost:,.0f} | 盈亏: {total_pnl:,.0f} ({total_pnl/total_cost*100:+.1f}%)\")\nprint(f\"股票数量: {len(results)}只\")\nprint(f\"\\n⚠️ 注: 现价基于4月1日收盘，与今日(4月8日)可能有差异\")\nPYEOF\n","timeout":120}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":117467,"output":1230,"cacheRead":19969,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":138666,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775665725849,"responseId":"0625b53e91bfda062d000a676fdbe367"}}
