{"type":"message","id":"a4483c45","parentId":"28415f89","timestamp":"2026-04-08T17:21:22.909Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a good picture of the system. Let me compile a comprehensive self-audit report based on all the information I've gathered.Let me structure this according to the user's requirements:\n\n1. **Problem Identification** - list specific issues with severity levels (high/medium/low)\n2. **Risk Analysis** -连锁反应\n3. **Optimization Suggestions** - actionable, specific recommendations\n4. **Summary** - core advantages, main weaknesses, priority recommendations\n\nKey findings from my exploration:\n\n**System Architecture (基础架构)**:\n- Single point of failure: data mounted on external hard drive (`/Volumes/A/openclaw-cold/...`) - if drive is not connected, system fails\n- Scripts are well organized in config/, scripts/, backtest/, execution/, risk/, research/\n\n**Strategy (策略模块)**:\n- Active strategy: \"smallcap_momentum_chip_breakout\" with 15.6% annual return, 36.31% max drawdown, Sharpe 1.161\n- Backtest shows strong metrics BUT there's a big gap between backtest (15.6%) and reality (-0.33% from earlier summary)\n- Walk-forward: quick version shows OOS Sharpe 0.822, but only 80 symbols - not fully validated\n- The real problem: the strategy hasn't been running in live trading - all live journals are empty\n\n**Data Module (数据模块)**:\n- Data is on external hard drive - single point of failure\n- The THS holdings sync works (skill found 3 accounts) but market value data seems inconsistent\n- Real-time data fetching issues - akshare returns matching prices to cost prices (meaning data is stale)\n\n**Risk Control (风控模块)**:\n- Risk engine has Pydantic validation\n- Has all the standard rules: max_single_weight, add_delisted_stocks, enforce_liquidity, etc.\n- BUT real-time risk gates (market_breadth, style_rotation) are filtering out all signals\n\n\n- There's a critical disconnect: the risk system is operational and actively blocking trades, yet the execution layer remains inactive\n\n**Operations & Monitoring (运维与监控)**:\n- cron scripts configured but appears inactive\n- live_execution_brief shows \"口径异常\" - inconsistent data sources\n- holdings_date = 20260401 but trade_date = 20260408 - 7 days stale\n- Real-time data: \"实时报价命中: 0 / miss: 0\" \"分时MA例外: 0 (data hit/miss=\"0/0\")\" - no real-time data at all\n\n**投研组织架构** (R&D Organization):\n- A single-user operation - no formal team structure\n- Documented clearly in README.md with good scripts and pipeline organization\n- No formalized review or knowledge management system exists beyond personal notes\n","thinkingSignature":"46ffcab6fae2c3c429e07ef82a9a636e81e20030bf9e0dbf0079c028c23390b8"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_zpwua5dyfe15_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system && ls -la logs/ | tail -15","timeout":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":922,"output":636,"cacheRead":67344,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":68902,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775668867074,"responseId":"0625c18313a34ce47dc44e55c2e213e1"}}
