{"type":"message","id":"7a9fb092","parentId":"fb78c88f","timestamp":"2026-04-08T17:21:46.761Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a comprehensive understanding of the system. Let me compile the audit report with all the findings.\n\nKey findings:\n1. **系统架构问题**：\n   - 数据依赖外置硬盘（data -> /Volumes/A/...），断开会丢数据\n   - 策略版本管理混乱，strategy_registry_v2.json 有多个策略状态不明\n   - 实盘报告停在4月8日，持仓数据过时\n\n2. **策略模块问题**：\n   - active_strategy 回测：年化15.6%，夏普1.161，最大回撤36.31%\n   - Walk-Forward 结果（quick版本）：IS年化-3.2%，夏普-0.29；OOS年化27.97%，夏普0.82 — 巨大的IS vs OOS差异！\n   - 有5个策略在_registry中，状态混乱\n   \n3. **数据模块**：\n   - 数据源来自akshare，需验证准确性\n   - 数据清洗流程不明确\n   - 外置硬盘依赖\n\n4. **风控模块**：\n   - risk_engine.py实现了Pydantic校验\n   - 但实盘风控有四大门控：market_breadth, style_rotation, volatility_regime, liquidity_regime\n   - broker_api.enabled = false，实际用的是simulated模拟盘\n\n5. **运维监控**：\n   - 日志覆盖不全，最后更新在4月6日\n   - 缺少实时监控体系\n   - 没有结构化的故障复盘流程\n\n6. **投研组织**：\n   - 这是一个人运营的系统，没有正式的投研团队配置\n   - 角色定义有research_owner, risk_owner, execution_owner, cto_delegate，但实际上只有用户自己在管理\n   - 文档和流程都是结构化的，但一个人执行所有职责\n\nI need to organize this into a comprehensive audit report.\n","thinkingSignature":"f6842360150ccc86d432955dbac898f708db00ee5c7c3dcf8ebeda2eb1e30ca6"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_gbczp8hkbzye_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system && cat research/reports/live_journal_v1_20260408.csv && echo \"---\" && head -5 research/reports/paper_nav_curve_v1.csv","timeout":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":1382,"output":470,"cacheRead":68832,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":70684,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775668893404,"responseId":"0625c19d9f30dc10b2b209e960f0cab5"}}
