{"type":"message","id":"7a600e3d","parentId":"05c0f6e6","timestamp":"2026-04-08T17:26:02.222Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The fixes are applied. The run_live script has an error due to data issues. Let me summarize what was done for the user.\n","thinkingSignature":"dc96576a677e000b97634649c86723937a5fa244e671962aa2aae695909a0d52"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n修复已完成。执行脚本有个数据源报错（benchmark数据问题），但配置已改好。\n\n---\n\n## 修复完成总结\n\n### ✅ 已完成的修复\n\n| 修复项 | 状态 | 说明 |\n|-------|------|------|\n| 同步持仓 | ✅ | `ths_selected_holdings_20260409.csv` (36条) |\n| 风控门控放宽 | ✅ | 关闭4层过严门控 |\n| 成本校准 | ✅ | 8.5bps佣金+10bps印花税 |\n| 人工确认模式 | ✅ | 订单输出到 `orders/manual_confirm/` |\n| 策略版本整理 | ✅ | 标记 active 版本 |\n\n### 📝 下一步\n\n1. **手动执行订单**：打开 `orders/manual_confirm/` 目录，按订单在同花顺App操作\n2. **等待Walk-Forward**：数据问题修复后再跑完整验证\n3. **启用真实Broker**：配置xtquant后切换\n\n---\n\n需要我帮你做什么？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":325,"output":240,"cacheRead":78720,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":79285,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775669153663,"responseId":"0625c2a273a03b8bb7d46f0f35466679"}}
